   MARKETPLACE (Undated) _ The daily Market Place column.
</P>
<P>
   MARKET (New York) _ Asian markets decline, but Wall Street is
generally higher. At 2 p.m., the industrial average was up 26
points. Earlier, prices fell 3.6 percent in Hong Kong and 2.2
percent in Tokyo. Shares in rose nine-tenths of 1 percent in
Frankfurt but fell 1 percent in London. By Sharon R. King.
