<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-01 16:50 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8775 &Cx1f; sci-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SCI-DRUG-MISUSE-ART-(     06-01 1049
