</P>
<P>
   Dorothy Q. Thomas, 38, New York, a human rights advocate and
women's rights leader, $245,000.
</P>
<P>
   Mary Zimmerman, 37, Evanston, Ill., a director and playwright
who adapts seemingly untheatrical source material from classic
world literature, $240,000.
</P>
